9zyLGAhHxb3C42FkANRsxCuVKAxQAQvhnem5s3QQ.name: Draconic Egg
9zyLGAhHxb3C42FkANRsxCuVKAxQAQvhnem5s3QQ.description: With a shell as sharp as a razor blade, the Draconic Egg sends a warning to novice Seekers, cautioning them about the power concealed within.

8nLBJaFaXcMSS2RK4YCGcHLxQuikK3aAPN1EZ3Uo.name: Everglade Egg
8nLBJaFaXcMSS2RK4YCGcHLxQuikK3aAPN1EZ3Uo.description: Found deep in the murky swamps, the Everglade Eggs have mutated to camouflage themselves amongst the creeping moss and fungus.

8XaR7cPaMZoMXWBWgeRcyjWRpKYpvGsPF6dMwxnV.name: Genesis Egg
8XaR7cPaMZoMXWBWgeRcyjWRpKYpvGsPF6dMwxnV.description: So much power in such a tiny egg. Should go well with some bacon.

CRMoQEu2B23vDYhiNPWBpCtf1dPxjsp7X9BcYxgb.name: Prairie Egg
CRMoQEu2B23vDYhiNPWBpCtf1dPxjsp7X9BcYxgb.description: Prairie Eggs thrive in dry heat and are often found in the tall grass - whatever's inside may share attributes with this unique environment...

EzcjkPxbnDRrCQytMD3BeX1UxT87wsEbLFbtSHWu.name: Quantum Egg
EzcjkPxbnDRrCQytMD3BeX1UxT87wsEbLFbtSHWu.description: The Quantum Egg stands as an enigmatic marvel, its shiny shell mirroring the colours of far-off and incredible places, teasing at the everchanging mysterious creature tucked inside...

yuZH8u6CnVWJhMsG6aYYbnBpNr6AzcMzcKZpsvKQ.name: Cliff Egg
yuZH8u6CnVWJhMsG6aYYbnBpNr6AzcMzcKZpsvKQ.description: These eggs are tough to crack, but from within, emerge only the strongest Nefties!

6A7kJVCqYuorjTEXvBFgsebkZ7f6xSTE12KE3YML.name: Festive Egg
6A7kJVCqYuorjTEXvBFgsebkZ7f6xSTE12KE3YML.description: Crack open the Festive egg to enjoy a cheerful melody guaranteed to put a smile on everyone's face.

HctGCLdrDtrJctH4znsPyvwi8uautGZqKyYCGvs5.name: Bloomer Egg
HctGCLdrDtrJctH4znsPyvwi8uautGZqKyYCGvs5.description: This egg emanates a sweet fragrance, enchanting all who catch a whiff, but where did it come from? No one knows, yet it captivates all who see it!

D33dBvERD1YYDRe5amEwucBUZNZHvsikReYHfH4t.name: Leaf Egg
D33dBvERD1YYDRe5amEwucBUZNZHvsikReYHfH4t.description: Layers of lush green leaves intricately weave together to encase this egg, creating mesmerizing patterns across its surface.

Dm9fiHHkDibZWZ27BUhJmYmVUK1QXxvUJCgTDvMQ.name: Clover Egg
Dm9fiHHkDibZWZ27BUhJmYmVUK1QXxvUJCgTDvMQ.description: The Clover egg is a symbol of good fortune. It promises luck to those who find one, making it highly coveted among Seekers.

9GjjF8C9rHbBMPdfq2bT1Y5rPVw6KK4CbqrQstxX.name: Marsh Egg
9GjjF8C9rHbBMPdfq2bT1Y5rPVw6KK4CbqrQstxX.description: The marsh egg, formed from swamp vegetation, appears delicate yet sturdy, giving way slightly to pressure while retaining its shape.

5JcYy8A1Cdjyt3RPU2itHo7Y11nTkTN8xaCCKbd2.name: Moss Egg
5JcYy8A1Cdjyt3RPU2itHo7Y11nTkTN8xaCCKbd2.description: This egg is made entirely of bright green moss. When touched, its surface feels velvety, releasing a subtle earthy scent that attracts those nearby.

uMJpxbmvG9rwU385QVsrrAA8qCsj2jT7zpakN7it.name: Aurora Egg
uMJpxbmvG9rwU385QVsrrAA8qCsj2jT7zpakN7it.description: The Aurora egg intrigues with its almost otherworldly appearance. A gentle chill hints at what it holds within, beckoning those brave enough to touch it.

4pkBzAn4TB9qWQWk4FeczpMmZfVbyhvzAWt8ZLfN.name: Frost Egg
4pkBzAn4TB9qWQWk4FeczpMmZfVbyhvzAWt8ZLfN.description: The swirling frost patterns beneath the egg's translucent surface refract light in a hypnotizing display of colors.

tkkf39Qebyp7LFg1yc9Fs7qW4N19P7BVPB4nxeoQ.name: Dune Egg
tkkf39Qebyp7LFg1yc9Fs7qW4N19P7BVPB4nxeoQ.description: The Dune egg may look as if your hand could pass through it with the lightest touch, yet too much pressure dislodges particles and inhaling these causes hallucinations.

9mAFm3DKg37bab6pQRq17Zcxpw4jDJCYJpgecmjV.name: Mirage Egg
9mAFm3DKg37bab6pQRq17Zcxpw4jDJCYJpgecmjV.description: This precious egg presents a challenge to find as its illusory nature causes some to perceive it as a gem nestled within the landscape, while others mistake it for a mere rock formation.
